                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="nav__toggle" id="nav-toggle">
                <i class='bx bx-menu'></i>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="l-main">


        <!--===== form =====-->
        <section class="contact section" id="contact">
            <h2 class="section-title">Let's get started</h2>

            <div class="contact__container bd-grid">
                <h2>Here's the process</h2>

                <ol>
                    <li>Within 24 hours, we'll reach out to start the journey of creating your special song.</li>
                    <li>You'll share your personal story, feelings, and any specific ideas for the song.</li>
                    <li>Our team will turn your story into a beautiful melody from your heart.</li>
                    <li>We'll show you the composition, and you can tell us if you like it or want any changes. It's
                        important to us that the song reflects your emotions perfectly.</li>
                    <li>After your approval, we'll create the song with love and care, ready to be treasured forever.
                    </li>
                    <li>You'll receive your song within a week.</li>
                </ol>
                <br><br><br>

                <form id="paymentForm" method="post" action="/submitPaymentData">
                    <label for="fullName">Full Name:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="fullName" name="fullName" required>

                    <label for="email">Email:</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>

                    <label for="trackType">Track Type:</label>
                    <div class="radio-group">

                        <input type="radio" id="trackType1" name="trackType" value="1" checked>
                        <label for="trackType1">Acoustic and Soothing (1 - 2 min duration) - Rs. 1800</label>
                        <br><br>
                        <input type="radio" id="trackType2" name="trackType" value="2">
                        <label for="trackType2">Professional - Studio Quality Track (2 - 3 min duration) - Rs.
                            2499</label>
                        <br><br>
                        <input type="radio" id="trackType3" name="trackType" value="3">
                        <label for="trackType3">Bollywood Style - Best for Weddings (3 - 4 min duration) - Rs.
                            4999</label>
                    </div>

                    <label for="whatsappNumber">WhatsApp Number:</label>
                    <input type="tel" id="whatsappNumber" name="whatsappNumber" required>

                    <button type="submit">Submit</button>
                </form>
                <br><br><br><br>
                <p>
                    <strong>Note:</strong>
                    To secure your custom song creation, we kindly request a 50% payment in advance. This helps us
                    ensure a seamless process and dedicate our full attention to crafting a unique musical experience
                    just for you. Your satisfaction remains at the core of our commitment, and we're dedicated to making
                    your musical journey truly unforgettable.
                    <br>Payment methods - UPI or Bank transfer!
                </p>
            </div>

        </section>


    </main>

